ing: 2 whole fresh jalapeno peppers, seeded, deveined and minced
1 (1 ounce) package dry ranch salad dressing mix
des: "Creamy Jalapeno is great for dipping veggies and chips. I make it for my family each week.  We love it for dipping tortilla chips."
ins: Place minced jalapenos, sour cream, ranch dressing mix, garlic powder, and cilantro in a blender or food processor. Blend until smooth. Cover and refrigerate at least one hour, or overnight, before serving.
